# Style and Theme - Bulgarian Legal AI Assistant

## Overview
The Bulgarian Legal AI Assistant features a modern, ChatGPT-inspired design system optimized for legal professionals and general users. This document outlines the comprehensive style guide, theme specifications, and UI component standards.

## Design Philosophy

### 1. Core Design Principles
- **Professional Accessibility**: Clean, trustworthy interface suitable for legal professionals
- **Modern Minimalism**: ChatGPT-inspired clean aesthetic with focused functionality
- **Bulgarian Legal Context**: Culturally appropriate design for Bulgarian users
- **Responsive Excellence**: Seamless experience across all device types
- **Cognitive Load Reduction**: Simplified interface reducing user mental overhead

### 2. Visual Hierarchy
```
Primary Focus: Chat Interface (Legal Q&A)
    ↓
Secondary: Search Controls (Methodology, Filters)
    ↓
Tertiary: Status Indicators (Connection, Processing)
    ↓
Supporting: Branding Elements (Logo, Footer)
```

