## Accessibility Standards

### 1. Color Contrast
- **AA Compliance**: All text meets WCAG 2.1 AA standards
- **Primary Green**: 4.5:1 contrast ratio with white text
- **Gray Text**: Minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio with backgrounds

### 2. Focus Management
```css
/* Focus Indicators */
.focusable:focus {
    outline: 2px solid var(--primary-green);
    outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Focus Within */
.input-wrapper:focus-within {
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--primary-green-light);
}
```

### 3. Screen Reader Support
- **ARIA Labels**: All interactive elements have appropriate ARIA labels
- **Semantic HTML**: Proper heading hierarchy and semantic structure
- **Alt Text**: All icons and images include descriptive alt text

